                            <comment id="16894610" author="ralph.goers@dslextreme.com" created="Sun, 28 Jul 2019 03:29:55 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;I have made Log4j Core optional at runtime. It is still required for the build and some functionality will be lost if it is not present but it should still be sufficient for most applications.&lt;/p&gt;

